00:40:22,150 --> 00:40:23,000
Masuklah.

501
00:40:32,800 --> 00:40:34,040
Lepas saja maskermu.

502
00:40:34,630 --> 00:40:35,520
Kau takkan menulariku.

503
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:37,800
Tapi aneh juga.

504
00:40:38,080 --> 00:40:39,480
Kita sudah divaksin campak,

505
00:40:39,560 --> 00:40:41,040
