525
00:41:36,910 --> 00:41:38,790
Wu Yan, maaf.

526
00:41:38,870 --> 00:41:40,360
Aku mengundurkan diri

527
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:41,640
tanpa memberitahumu.

528
00:41:42,950 --> 00:41:45,630
Aku tahu harapanmu padaku tinggi,
tapi aku

529
00:41:45,720 --> 00:41:46,670
Tak usah dibahas lagi.

530
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:48,600
Aku terdengar seperti seorang konselor.

531
00:41:51,390 --> 00:41:52,280
Aku mengerti.

532
00:41:53,390 --> 00:41:55,230
