538
00:42:08,520 --> 00:42:09,870
Tapi kau dan Wei Hao...

539
00:42:10,670 --> 00:42:11,840
Bukankah aku sudah bilang...

540
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:12,960
Sudahlah.

541
00:42:13,040 --> 00:42:14,080
Jangan kau ungkit lagi.

542
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:15,320
Kenapa?

543
00:42:15,800 --> 00:42:17,910
Bukankah kau tahu jelas
keadaan keluargaku?

544
00:42:18,320 --> 00:42:19,800
Orang tua tak bisa dipilih.

545
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:21,390
Aku memang kesal,

546
00:42:21,470 --> 00:42:22,680
